Revision history for Log-Any-IfLOG

0.08    2016-06-16 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Rename internal dumb object class to avoid clash with
	  Object::Dumb.


0.07    2015-08-17 (PERLANCAR)

	- Fix get_logger().


0.06    2015-08-17 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add get_logger() static method.


0.05    2015-04-05 (PERLANCAR)

	- Pass to Log::Any if Log::Any is already loaded.

        - Add variable: $ENABLE_LOG to force enable/disable logging.


0.04    2015-04-02 (PERLANCAR)

	- Return a singleton instead of a new dumb object everytime.


0.03    2015-04-02 (PERLANCAR)

	- [ux] Also load Log::Any if TRACE/DEBUG/VERBOSE/QUIET/LOG_LEVEL
	  envs are set.


0.02    2015-03-24 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [doc] Expand on the rationale for the module.


0.01    2015-02-21 (PERLANCAR)

        - First release.
